text: Subnational or sub-national may refer to: * Subnational administrative division, a type of administrative division, under the national level * Subnational legislature, a type of regional legislature, under the national level * Subnational state, a type of state, under the national level * Subnational diplomacy, a form of diplomacy, under the national level * Subnational flag, a flag of an entity under the national level ==See also== * Supranational (disambiguation) * International (disambiguation) * Multinational (disambiguation) * Transnational (disambiguation) * National (disambiguation)
title: Subnational
